The '''fawn-breasted thrush''' ('''''Zoothera machiki''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Turdidae]]. It is [[endemic]] to the [[Tanimbar Islands]] in [[Indonesia]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]].

